        <strow class="- topic/strow " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="strow:5;96:16">
          <stentry class="- topic/stentry " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="stentry:9;97:20"><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="b:19;97:23">Storage Policy</b></stentry>
          <stentry class="- topic/stentry " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="stentry:10;98:20">Storage policies allow you to differentiate how the objects are stored in the
              cluster.<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="p:9;99:26">You require a different name for the Storage Policy. If so, edit the
