        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="li:17;316:13">Start with a system that is closer to your final anticipated system size â€“ this means
          you can use a high partition power that suites your final system.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <ul class="- topic/ul " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="ul:9;320:9">
      <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\ring_specifications.dita" xtrc="li:18;321:11">You can add additional storage policies as the system grows. These storage policies can
